      <ul>
        <li>Permitting online advertising.</li>
        <li>Encouraging the private sector to invest.</li>
        <li>Expanding the pool of potential investors.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="span4 obama">
      <%= image_tag('obama.jpg', alt: "Obama", title: "Obama") %>
      <div class= "obama-text">
